content:
FlexCards supports versioning and cloning.

PURPOSE
To update a FlexCard already published on Lightning or Community pages, and elsewhere (Version), 
or make slight modifications to an existing FlexCard (Version), 
or create a new FlexCard but copy over layout, settings, or both (Clone).

FlexCards Versioning: You can create an identical copy of a FlexCard by creating a new version with the same name, author, but with a new version number. Create a new version when you want to make slight modifications to a published FlexCard.

FlexCards Cloning: You can create a new FlexCard by cloning a current one, updating the Author and/or Name, and copying over layout and/or settings.

Follow requirements when naming FlexCards and FlexCard elements to prevent errors.
